reviewText: One of the few products I rate with 5 stars. I thought the story was interesting, a little zany at times, and moving at times. Good acting. After watching it, I wanted to see other dramas that the main actors were in. I enjoyed watching it.
In my opinion one of the better Korean Dramas. Good quality DVDs and good English subtitles. Stay away from the really cheap DVD sets I find that they usually junk or ripped copies.
